snippet.title: B&N - Picture Perfect Golf - 1996
snippet.description:
For those who wants to rememorate this golf game that was Picture Perfect Golf (also known as Picture Perfect Golf: The Prince Course) developed by B&N Companies, Inc., but published by Enteractive, Inc. in 1996.
